A vintage 1960s corporate illustration style depicting a futuristic office transformation: a sleek mid-century modern workspace where floating holographic screens and interconnected glowing nodes orbit around a central curved desk, replacing rows of identical boxy computers. Workers in retro-futuristic attire interact with dynamic, colorful data streams that flow organically between workstations like ribbons of light. The scene has warm amber and teal tones with bold geometric shapes, muted paper textures, and the optimistic aesthetic of vintage tech advertisements. Singapore's Marina Bay skyline visible through large windows, rendered in stylized atomic-age illustration technique with halftone dot patterns and limited color palette.
